{"tid":410744,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個廢老親戚無理取鬧事件","createTime":"2017-09-23T07:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T21:12:12.000Z","uid":104748,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c1eb120b3414b3a86d5a9af5ea198a0d7d9eb9","tid":410744,"uid":104748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"有日飲茶例牌底聽啲廢老親戚廢嗡<br />\n咁啱講開有個姑媽近排身體唔好<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  親戚A<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我 : 邊個姑媽？(事關我有4個姑媽)<br />\n親戚A : 廢話！你有好多個姑媽咩？<br />\n我 : 問下都鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼知咩<br />\n親戚A : 等你的救命死得啦<br />\n<br />\n隔咗一陣 到講開有個表哥拍拖<br />\n<br />\n我 : 聽講表哥好似識咗個女朋友<br />\n親戚A : 邊個表哥？(事關我有5個表哥)<br />\n(依刻 我露出咗夜神月嘅眼神 : 機會嚟啦)<br />\n我 : 廢話！你有好多個姪仔咩？<br />\n親戚A : 一啲禮貌都無！咁同長輩講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我當堂啤一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有無啲親戚都幾無理取鬧？"},{"pid":"56af8ef8baa6db843ef558ff7c02c0d660a7dd42","tid":410744,"uid":104748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"廢老偷偷留下負皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06983e5548b5dc307a6c7ef3b5a990cfbed69768","tid":410744,"uid":6073,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"唔知算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我阿姨見到我就話「你成日唔番工因住比人炒呀！請著你呢啲咪陰功囉 邊有人咁樣成日唔番工架！你地班後生冇啲責任心 香港靠你地等死啦」<br />\n<br />\n我番份工要企 <br />\n而佢鬧我果時我因爲工傷要坐輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fdffaf15face69e848a39ea18e620b8754ea61","tid":410744,"uid":35746,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T08:28:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ac8b2ca14a77e0902ff2f60cc5cb6227ea6919